{"tid":1874644,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「緊急」機場禁區變隔離營無人講","createTime":"2020-02-11T10:18:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T14:56:20.000Z","uid":277115,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d5b633b7031d2739f5532ef40759b4ec1fd60234","tid":1874644,"uid":277115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T10:18:49.000Z","msg":"移記爆料，依家機場禁區好危險。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩唔俾入境？响機場禁區住多幾日，等過左14日先過關，就可以入境唔使隔離啦！<br />\n<br />\n依家好多大陸人都識咁玩，又奈佢唔何<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，飛完外國再飛香港，當佢十日前响大陸出發？無問題&hellip;响禁區住幾日先入境香港就得啦！<br />\n<br />\n裡面啲餐廳坐滿大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，其間帶病傳俾其他人一啲唔出奇，咁大個漏洞無人知無人理&hellip;依家機場做野嘅人人自危，其他旅客完全唔知自己有幾危險！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83257a3d6e6af5c450775b11cfcbe84fd3b8b851","tid":1874644,"uid":277115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T10:21:18.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"0bf74d481db09e2ce640c64d34905ab8d182f2e4","tid":1874644,"uid":277115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T10:21:39.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"435101f3d8d3a71c7b947aaecfebe162e247fab0","tid":1874644,"uid":277115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T10:21:49.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"ca2e1449a572410777b41385e0434ab63fdd30d8","tid":1874644,"uid":277115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T10:21:59.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"7c0bc102179dbba1c37ee06993d7e6cb2e68dfd8","tid":1874644,"uid":277115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T10:22:13.000Z","msg":"自推5"},{"pid":"d5d0f09d0314b43873efd0c82c93b3aff045090c","tid":1874644,"uid":277115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T10:22:25.000Z","msg":"自推6"},{"pid":"4edb7edcd5d6ad1bf7454a68f4f264ae7dddc52a","tid":1874644,"uid":277115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2